'''''Star Wars Insider'' 58''' is the fifty-eighth issue of ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' magazine. It was released to newsstands on [[February 5]], [[2002]].

==Contents==
===Departments===
*"[[Rebel Rumblings]]"
*"[[Prequel Update|''Attack of the Clones'' Update]] with [[Rick McCallum]]" {{C|by [[Dan Madsen]]}}
*"[[Star News]]: From the World of Lucasfilm" {{C|by Scott Chernoff}}
*"[[Behind the Magic]]" &mdash; Watto You Looking at? {{C|by [[Rob Coleman]]}}
*"[[Gamescape]]" &mdash; The ''Core Rules'' Strike Back! {{C|by [[Christopher Perkins]] with [[Dave Gross]]}}
*"[[Bookshelf]]" &mdash; Flirting with the Dark Side {{C|by [[Daniel Wallace]]}}
*"[[Comics Link]]" &mdash; Bounty Hunters: We Don't Need Their Scum {{C|by Daniel Wallace}}
*"[[Set Piece]]: The Death Star Trash Compactor" {{C|by [[Chris Trevas|Christopher Trevas]] & [[Chris Reiff]]}}
*"[[Scouting the Galaxy]]" &mdash; Super Collector Surprise at Celebration II {{C|by [[Stephen J. Sansweet]]}}
*"[[Crossword (department)|Crossword]]" {{C|by [[Michael Selinker]]}}
*"[[Star Wars Q&A|''Star Wars'' Q&A]]" {{C|by [[Pablo Hidalgo]]}}
*"[[The Last Page]]"

===Features===
*"[[Joel Edgerton: Lars Attacks]]" {{C|by [[Scott Chernoff]]}}
*:<small>[[Joel Edgerton]] shows us what [[Owen|Uncle Owen]] was like before he became a grumpy old man.</small>
*"[[Bonnie Piesse: Micro Beru]]" Interview {{C|by Scott Chernoff}}
*:<small>[[Bonnie Maree Piesse|Bonnie Piesse]] talks about inhabiting the role of [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker's]] Aunt [[Beru Whitesun Lars/Legends|Beru]] and how visiting [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]] is far more daunting than working at the circus.</small>
*"[[Billy Dee Williams: An Eclectic Career]]" Interview {{C|by [[Helen Keir]] with [[Allen Varney]]}}
*:<small>Most fans know [[Billy Dee Williams]] as the smooth [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]], but there's far more to the creative talents of this veteran actor.</small>
*"[[Art Wars: Art of the Star Wars Trading Card Game|Art Wars: Art of the ''Star Wars'' Trading Card Game]]" {{C|by [[Michael G. Ryan]]}}
*:<small>The new ''[[Star Wars]]'' trading [[Star Wars Customizable Card Game|card game]] includes an early look at images from [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Attack of the Clones'']].</small>
*"[[New Heirs to the Empire: The Fighting 501st]]" {{C|by Michael G. Ryan}}
*:<small>[[501st Legion (fan organization)|A legion of fans]] prefer the glorious [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire]] to the scrappy [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebellion]], at least when it comes to making a fashion statement.</small>

